    <div style="padding: 5% 10%; color: #1b9eee;">
        <h2 class="pb-5">About Orion</h2>
        <h3 style="font-size: 3rem;">Let us introduce ourselves.</h3>
        <div class="about-us p-3 pt-5">
            <p>Welcome to Orion, a vibrant community dedicated to <b>academic
                    excellence,
                    innovation, and personal
                    growth</b>. At Orion, we believe that education goes beyond textbooks—it’s about fostering a
                dynamic
                environment where students thrive both inside and outside the classroom.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our campus is equipped with <b>state-of-the-art facilities</b>, including modern classrooms,
                well-stocked
                libraries, advanced laboratories, and collaborative study spaces. We also offer a variety of
                extracurricular
                activities, from student clubs to sports, ensuring a well-rounded college experience.
            </p>
            <p>
                Beyond academics, we take pride in our inclusive and supportive community. With <b>diverse student
                    organizations, mentorship programs, and career guidance</b>, we help students build lasting
                connections and
                prepare for future success.
            </p>
            <p>
                Join us at Orion, where knowledge meets opportunity, and every student is empowered to achieve
                their goals. Together, we shape a future of innovation, leadership, and lifelong learning.
            </p>
            <style>
                .about-us p {
