                }

                .courses-content h3 {
                    color: black !important;
                    font-size: 1.5rem;
                }
            </style>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin: 0 10% 10% ; padding: 5%; background-color: #0b6298; color: white;">
        <h3 class="mb-5" style="font-size: 3rem; color: yellow;">Orion College Mission</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Orion College prepares students for lives of personal and professional
            distinction and meaningful engagement
            with the world. The college extends this mission by offering graduate and adult programs to all learners.
            Inspired by its values of inclusivity, collaboration, and a commitment to lifelong learning, Orion College
            fosters an environment that encourages academic excellence and personal growth. Through active and
            collaborative learning, the college equips students with the skills and knowledge needed to succeed in their
            careers and contribute meaningfully to society.</p>
        <h3 class="my-5" style="font-size: 3rem; color: yellow;">Vision</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Orion College envisions a dynamic learning community that empowers students to excel academically, grow
        personally, and lead with integrity. Through innovation, inclusivity, and collaboration, we strive to cultivate
        future leaders who contribute meaningfully to society and drive positive change in an ever-evolving.</p>
